BURBY, Respondent, v. ROOME, Appellant. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. April 2, 1894.) Action by Sarah J. Burby against William J. Roome. Motion for reargument, 27 N. Y. Supp. 250.

Argued before DALY, C. J., and BISCHOFF and PRYOR. JJ.

PER CURIAM.

The motion fails to comply with Rule 16 of this court Denied, with $10 costs.
